title: Jagannath
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, International, Buffet, Fast food, Take-out
description: Established veggie cafe, restaurant, and health food shop 10 minutes from Red Square, . Food is mostly vegan and are labeled in Russian. Very little English spoken. Pay for food by weight buffet style set up. Wi-Fi zone. Some internet PCs available (pay at the check out).
